    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>REMOTE VOTING</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Anne Ruderman</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Ruderman, Anne</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>New Jersey State Government Committee approves bill that would permit ill members to be considered fully present in determining quorum and allow them to vote on legislation through unspecified 'remote electronic means' (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A bill that would allow ill state legislators to participate in house and committee meetings and vote on legislation through unspecified ''remote electronic means'' passed through the Senate State Government Committee this week. The bill would permit ill members to be considered fully present and would count their presence toward determining a quorum.</p>
        <p>Anne Ruderman</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
